00:03:08.830 --> 00:03:15.040
He was with MSNBC, writing
about lifestyles and wine.

00:03:15.040 --> 00:03:17.380
He's also been published
in the New York

00:03:17.380 --> 00:03:20.110
Times, and various
food magazines

00:03:20.110 --> 00:03:21.930
and tabloid magazines.

00:03:21.930 --> 00:03:24.500
So he is really knowledgeable.

00:03:24.500 --> 00:03:28.210
And we did many a
series of stories,

00:03:28.210 --> 00:03:30.200
together, that we
loved doing, which

00:03:30.200 --> 00:03:33.970
was finding wines to
