00:42:27.990 --> 00:42:30.150
And I bring some
form of Cabernet-

00:42:30.150 --> 00:42:32.400
based Franc wine--
Cabernet Franc-based wine,

00:42:32.400 --> 00:42:34.597
everywhere I can,
